{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">liftLooseBVarsS</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Lifts loose bound variables `>= s` in `e` by `d`.\nIt assumes the input is maximally shared, and ensures the output is too.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS","kind":"def","line":53,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.lean#L53-L55"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS'\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">liftLooseBVarsS'</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareBuilder.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Internal.AlphaShareBuilderM\">Internal.AlphaShareBuilderM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Lifts loose bound variables `>= s` in `e` by `d`.\nIt assumes the input is maximally shared, and ensures the output is too.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS'","kind":"def","line":36,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.liftLooseBVarsS'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.lean#L36-L51"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">lowerLooseBVarsS</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Lowers the loose bound variables `>= s` in `e` by `d`.\nThat is, a loose bound variable `bvar i` with `i >= s` is mapped to `bvar (i-d)`.\nIt assumes the input is maximally shared, and ensures the output is too.\nRemark: if `s < d`, then the result is `e`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS","kind":"def","line":32,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.lean#L32-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS'\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">lowerLooseBVarsS'</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareBuilder.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Internal.AlphaShareBuilderM\">Internal.AlphaShareBuilderM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Lowers the loose bound variables `>= s` in `e` by `d`.\nThat is, a loose bound variable `bvar i` with `i >= s` is mapped to `bvar (i-d)`.\nIt assumes the input is maximally shared, and ensures the output is too.\nRemark: if `s < d`, then the result is `e`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS'","kind":"def","line":13,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.lowerLooseBVarsS'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/LooseBVarsS.lean#L13-L30"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM","Lean.Meta.Sym.ReplaceS"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.LooseBVarsS"}